overview: Nikki & Desire Moore: Even a hectic day at the office doesn't stop Nikki from lusting after Desire Moore's young tasty body... Honney Bunny & Wanda Lust:  Wanda came over to hang out with Honney Bunny's mom, but she was nowhere to be found, so Wanda took the opportunity to get to know Honney Bunny... Crystal Kats & Sharon:  Sharon just got her first laptop and asked Crystal to help her set it up. She was soon lapping at something else... Kitty & Kayla Quinn:  Kitty isn't living up to the standards of the cheer squad, and Coach Kayla plans on going to extremes to whip her back into shape.
title: Her First Older Woman 2
